  "description": "CaffeeScore is a premium, enterprise-grade digital cupping form designed to modernize the specialty coffee evaluation process. Completely replacing standard paper workflows, it enforces the strict guidelines of the **SCA 2025 Coffee Value Assessment (CVA)** protocol while operating seamlessly without an internet connection in farms or roasting laboratories.",
